  | accessdate = 2007-03-15 }}
</ref> In [[1977]], the game was split into two versions: the simpler ''Dungeons & Dragons'' and the more complex '''''[[Editions_of_Dungeons_%26_Dragons#Advanced_Dungeons_.26_Dragons|Advanced Dungeons & Dragons]]''''' (abbreviated as '''''AD&D''''' or '''''ADnD''''').<ref>{{cite journal
  | last = Gygax
  | first = Gary
  | authorlink =Gary Gygax
  | coauthors =
  | title = From the Sorcer's Scroll: D&D®, AD&D® and Gaming
  | journal = [[Dragon (magazine)|The Dragon]] #26
