  | format =
  | doi =
  | accessdate = 2006-06-08 }}
</ref> Other licensed [[Miniature figure#Manufacturers|miniature manufacturers]] who produced official figures include [[Grenadier Miniatures]] (1980 - 1983),<ref>{{cite web
