* [http://home.flash.net/~brenfrow/ TSR Archive] &ndash; a catalogue of almost everything produced for all editions of D&D by TSR and other publishers.
* [http://www.acaeum.com/ The Acaeum] &ndash; detailed information on pre-AD&D2 (1989) editions of the game.
* [http://www.dragonsfoot.org/ Dragonsfoot] &ndash; Fan resource for earlier editions of the game, forums include several of early D&D creators, including Gary Gygax.
